{"pin":"BH00387","subcodes":[{"code":"BH00387","anchor":"","first_line":"O My Most Exalted Pen! Make mention of him who hath turned unto God on a day wherein most men have turned away, and hath quaffed the choice wine [3.5s]... ...It is evident that every age in which a Manifestation of God hath lived is divinely ordained, and may, in a sense, be characterized as God’s appointed Day","first_line_orig":"یا قلمی الاعلی اذکر من اقبل الی الله فی یوم فیه اعرض اکثر الناس و شرب الرحیق  ","language":"5","word_count":"1750","subjects":"@corruption; misinterpretation of the Word of God, @prayer for spiritual recognition, @the Bab; the Primal Point; station and claims of the Bab, @Seal of the Prophets, @transcendence; unknowability of God, @the Word of God; influence and centrality of","notes":" \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#386\"\u003eLL#386\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[],"writing_refs":[{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ar","lang_name":"Arabic"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"el","lang_name":"Greek"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"zh-Hant","lang_name":"Traditional Chinese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ja","lang_name":"Japanese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"ty